The '''Um'Tal''' was an ancient artifact of a lost civilization believed to be invested with mystical powers. Also known as the "Sky Stone", the Um'Tal was believed to have been located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Teh'Jar II]]. The search for the Um'Tal was undertaken by [[Doctor/Legends|Doctor]] [[Angrail Ryhl]] and his nemesis, [[Nardo Sau]].

